channel.title: Server offline? Move this topic to server help pls!
channel.description:
well i recently updated my source then just re opened after a litle change :/ its was on 78% online before now it is only 46 :/ idk wat is going on
can anny1 help me solving the problem?
oh and it keeps saying server offline after serveral months :(
[IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/2ds0mlt.png[/img]

item.title: Server offline? Move this topic to server help pls!
item.dc:creator: @Skrillex_Craft Skrillex_Craft
item.description:
@Skrillex_Craft wrote:

[quote=“sk8rdude461, post:4, topic:535634”][quote author=Skrillex_Craft link=topic=654441.msg4384462#msg4384462 date=1384805474]

This looks like a 317 loading higher revision, not a 508 (just letting you know).

Also, check your portforward. Make sure your IPv4 address didn’t change (the 192.168.X.X you put in your routers config)
[/quote]o lol i didnt know this was still open the problem is i cant enter my portforward on the host’s site since i need to pay my internet so actually its solved and euhm its a 552

There isn’t even a 552 deob or anything related out. So I don’t know where you’re getting that info but it seems wrong[/quote]there is no 552 server status on moparscape but it is a 552
